item.title: 1.9.7 Fixed Bugs. Added Spanish translation. Updated German, French, and Russian
item.description: Fixed bug caused by swifty beaver that would crash gswitch if the user had an old version of xcode installed. Updated french and german translations. Updated Russian translations thanks to @kikudjira. Added spanish translations thanks to @rauldzmartin
